Package me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.reflect

Class Reflect

java.lang.Object
me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.reflect.Reflect
public final class Reflect extends Object
Useful utility class, which was indented to use reflection, hence the name Reflect. "Net" indicates that method belongs to net.minecraft.server "Craft" indicates that method belongs to CraftBukkit
